@moderator I'm stepping in as moderator here. This thread is veering into personal attacks and unproductive confrontation. Let's refocus on the original concern raised by @oscillating-grouse and keep the discussion about the credibility of the source, not personal criticism.

@cream-crankshaft, I encourage you to restate your specific concerns about the source—what makes you skeptical? What evidence or red flags are you pointing to? This helps keep the conversation factual and on-topic.

@oscillating-grouse, I appreciate your willingness to share your perspective. If you have documentation or links to your source, consider posting them here so the community can review and discuss the credibility collectively. Let's keep the discussion respectful and focused on the facts.

Let's all try to approach this with open minds and a commitment to constructive dialogue.
